<H3> <TI>   Tokyo To Grant 1.11 Billion Yen to Benin </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2102141294 Tokyo KYODO in English 1339 GMT 21 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2102141294 </F>
