  [Text] Tokyo, April 25 KYODO -- Outgoing Foreign Minister 
Tsutomu Hata, who is virtually certain to become premier later 
in the day, repeated suggestions Monday that he may ask Social 
Democratic Party (SDP) Chairman Tomiichi Murayama to join the 
new cabinet. 
